OL,3,C'Cheers, drive!' - Why this bride took
OL,4,Ca bus to her wedding
OL,6,FA wheelchair user from Cardiff arrived
OL,7,Fat her wedding in unique style after
OL,8,Ftaking the bus on her big day.
OL,10,FSarah Tunnicliffe has muscular
OL,11,Fdystrophy - a rare genetic disease
OL,12,Fthat causes progressive muscle
OL,13,Fweakness.
