OL,3,C'Cheers, drive!' - Why this bride took
OL,4,Ca bus to her wedding
OL,6,FShe spoke to ITV Cymru Wales in July
OL,7,Fabout the challenges she faced in
OL,8,Ffinding a vehicle which could
OL,9,Faccommodate her powered wheelchair to
OL,10,Fthe ceremony. With few accessible
OL,11,Ftransport options, Sarah was left with
OL,12,Fthe prospect of taking public
OL,13,Ftransport to the venue.
OL,15,FAfter sharing her story with ITV Cymru
OL,16,FWales, the televised report resulted
OL,17,Fin people getting in touch from across
OL,18,Fthe UK.
