OL,3,C'Cheers, drive!' - Why this bride took
OL,4,Ca bus to her wedding
OL,6,F"We had some wonderful offers from
OL,7,Fover the border in England and
OL,8,FScotland", Sarah said, "I just want to
OL,9,Fsay a huge thank you to everybody who
OL,10,Fhelped, reached out and all the well-
OL,11,Fwishers as well".
OL,13,FBut there was one opportunity she
OL,14,Fcouldn't turn down. An offer from
OL,15,FCardiff Bus to put on a private
OL,16,Fservice to the wedding.
OL,18,F"It's a private bus, non-stop to the
OL,19,Fvenue", she said, "I thought it would
OL,20,Fbe a great story to tell as well. It's
OL,21,Fan unusual way - it's unique".
