OL,3,C'Cheers, drive!' - Why this bride took
OL,4,Ca bus to her wedding
OL,6,FSarah said there is a more serious
OL,7,Fside to her unusual transport choice.
OL,8,FJust over a third of disabled people
OL,9,Fin Wales are married, but campaigners
OL,10,Fsay the issues Sarah has faced aren't
OL,11,Fnew.
OL,13,FShe said, "The point is to highlight
OL,14,Fthat there aren't the accessible
OL,15,Fservices available in Cardiff.
OL,17,F"It seemed crazy to get a vehicle to
OL,18,Fdrive 105 miles to get here to take me
OL,19,Fand my other half down the road - a 10
OL,20,Fminute journey. I just couldn't accept
OL,21,Fit!"
