OL,3,C'Cheers, drive!' - Why this bride took
OL,4,Ca bus to her wedding
OL,6,FBut after arriving at the Royal Welsh
OL,7,FCollege of Music and Drama, Sarah and
OL,8,Fher new husband, Jamie, we able to
OL,9,Fenjoy their special day.
OL,11,F"I'm going to enjoy every minute of
OL,12,Fit", said Sarah. "I feel absolutely
OL,13,Famazing - the day has been absolutely
OL,14,Fwonderful.
OL,16,F"The ride on the bus getting here was
OL,17,Famazing - it's all in the planning!"
